  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "The suggested command for running remix & a local geth test node is: \r\n\r\n```\r\ngeth --rpc --rpccorsdomain=\"http://remix.ethereum.org\" --rpcapi web3,eth,debug,personal,net --vmdebug --datadir <path/to/local/folder/for/test/chain> --dev console\r\n```\r\n\r\nSome of these flags were recently deprecated, so this should be the new suggested command: \r\n\r\n```\r\ngeth --http --http.corsdomain=\"http://remix.ethereum.org\" --http.api web3,eth,debug,personal,net --vmdebug --datadir <path/to/local/folder/for/test/chain> --dev console\r\n```\r\n\r\n![Screen Shot 2020-07-02 at 6 38 18 PM](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/41963722/86387588-af91be00-bc93-11ea-8ab1-db48214cd256.png)\r\n",
